{"tid":1995543,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【Dramione/Feltson】妙麗馬份紅線計劃－一切由哈利波特開始","createTime":"2020-04-30T10:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T14:05:30.000Z","uid":304773,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b31f452032124045ed20dbea1e189a14eb2ebd97","tid":1995543,"uid":304773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T10:31:06.000Z","msg":"－－80%程度FF及學術討論－－<br />\n<br />\n1. Emma Watson承認係10-12歲時曾經暗戀Tom Felton，因為佢大佢幾年，係個壞男孩，重要成日帶個滑板去片場玩。由於Emma鍾意得太明顯，Tom知道咗之後，表示當佢係佢阿妹咁看待，Emma表示心痛。（字眼：Still DOES，意指今時今日依然心痛，woo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\nSource: Jonathan Ross Show<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SSshn6nGONs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSSshn6nGONs&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=59a7eb9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SSshn6nGONs</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 佢係第二個節目入面都有講過類似暗戀Tom嘅經歷<br />\nSource: 2009 Regis and Kelly<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fs5jYlTdmw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFs5jYlTdmw4&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=469dae60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fs5jYlTdmw4</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 哈利波特3時期，Emma 同 Tom 攞咗個disney award，係interview嘅時候，Emma表現緊張，周不時含情脈脈望住Tom講嘢。<br />\nSource: Tom Felton &amp; Emma Watson - Disney Awards 2004<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YuaL_GOdgDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYuaL_GOdgDg&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=3a792460\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YuaL_GOdgDg</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 哈利波特4－火盃的考驗，其中一場戲係舞會，Emma 同 Tom 係戲入面冇對手戲，卻係幕後拖手仔跳舞！當Emma 走咗去同 victor krum 跳舞時，Tom在旁邊道出「lucky man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」等羨慕字句。<br />\nSource: HP4 Behind the scenes (Yule Ball)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VACjGFpOc8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVACjGFpOc8I&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=956e5b7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VACjGFpOc8I</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 做咩拖手仔啫～<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WdLVP98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWdLVP98.png&h=6c63384c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. HP7 part 2 記者會，Emma被問到係戲入面有同榮恩哈利kiss，但其實會唔會都想同Tom kiss呢？Emma話Tom嘅女朋友今日都係度哈哈哈，12歲嘅我會想同佢kiss，但係21歲嘅我就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\nSource: 'Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Part 2' Press Conference<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WVV9GowGPaM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWVV9GowGPaM&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=c38cf5f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WVV9GowGPaM</a><br />\n<br />\n7. Tom竟然係南非教Emma彈結他？原來Emma都去咗南非玩，Emma重要著住件pyjama添<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PS6qsWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPS6qsWV.jpg&h=9a49d248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B1WDOOaAiYJ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1WDOOaAiYJ%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=176caaec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1WDOOaAiYJ%2F&h=eba3afc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B1WDOOaAiYJ/</a><br />\n<br />\n8. Emma Waston個IG post咗一幅同Tom頭貼頭合照，swipe left 之後仲隱藏咗一條一齊踩溫馨滑板班嘅影片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LcLrcq5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcLrcq5.jpg&h=0ec9402b&s={SIZ